606
00:40:54,186 --> 00:40:56,354
It's in your hands now.

607
00:40:57,957 --> 00:40:58,813
Hehe.

608
00:41:02,565 --> 00:41:05,880
Thank you. Let's take
a photo first. Come on.

609
00:41:06,171 --> 00:41:08,230
Come on, this way, please.

610
00:41:08,739 --> 00:41:11,362
