The real one is here now.

611
00:41:12,419 --> 00:41:13,566
Move closer, please.

612
00:41:14,349 --> 00:41:16,262
Okay, look at the camera.

613
00:41:16,262 --> 00:41:19,540
3, 2, 1. Move closer, please.

614
00:41:19,540 --> 00:41:21,307
Okay, here we go, 3, 2, 1.

615
00:41:21,307 --> 00:41:24,404
- Mini heart, please. Okay.
